pageContext.description:
//"The mind directs the body's power. I get it now." -- Basler
Through training, mindfulness, and practice, you've learned to use your own mind and body as a tool.
Chi lets you fight, move, and act with grace, power, and precision. You can push your own abilities past normal limits, or unlock new ones.

